divs: Sighting DetailsNoticed lighted object in NW sky from Olathe, KS. It seemed to be a plane until took notice of no typical flashing lights and it's slow hovering motion and side to side movements at times. Object in distance and hovering with small movements left to right. Object is still in NW sky and has only moved slightly north since 8:30 pm. Many planes have flown by proving how slow moving and how elevated this object really is. 10:45 pm currently. Proven to be Unable to show up on photo or video
Summary: Lighted object spotted in NW sky hovering small movements LT to RT still present 2.5 hours later
